These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-1::.
House: gothic-revival, modern, palace, townhouse, ranch-style
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, adventure, documentary, family, scientific
1. the person watching adventure movies is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is somewhere between the person watching scientific movies and the townhouse house##7
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the palace house##3
4. the gothic-revival house is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
6. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere between the modern house and the palace house##7
7. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the right of the townhouse house##5
8. the person watching documentary movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |        2        |      3       |     4      |      5      |
| House           | townhouse | palace | ranch-style | modern | gothic-revival    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | action          | scientific   | family     | documentary |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, almond-milk, juice, water
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, subway, train, trike
1. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
2. the person drinking water is between the person drinking coffee and the person driving the train##2
3. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person drinking water##5
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person drinking water is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person driving the roller##7
8. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |   3    |     4     |   5   |
| Beverage        | milk | coffee | water | almond-milk | juice  |
| Transport   | jet-ski   | roller   | subway | train     | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-3::.
There 5 different types of food: avocado, kiwi, lettuce, pineapple, pumpkin
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, tulip, lily, iris, marigold
1. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
2. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the left of the person who growslily##5
3. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere between the person who growstulip and the person who growsiris##7
4. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
5. the person eating avocado is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person eating pineapple##3
7. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the right of the person who growslily##5
8. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |     4     |    5    |
| Food          | lettuce  | pumpkin   | pineapple | kiwi      | avocado |
| Flower   | tulip | lily | begonia   | iris | marigold  |

