.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-4::.
There are 5 different nationalities: canadian, egyptian, german, japanese, spanish
5 different games are played: whist, poker, domino, mah-jongg, canasta
1. the person playing domino is somewhere between the spanish and the japanese##7
2. the egyptian is on the far right##1
3. the person playing poker is somewhere between the egyptian and the japanese##7
4. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
5. the canadian is on the left of the japanese##1
6. the person playing whist is on the far left or far right##3
7. the spanish is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |    5     |
| Nationality   | canadian | japanese | german | spanish    | egyptian |
| Game     | canasta     | mah-jongg     | domino | poker | whist     |

