1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
7. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere between the person watching action movies and the person drinking iced-tea##7
8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4      |     5     |
