.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-6::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, swisher, ritmeester, blend, chaman
5 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, hamster, rabbit, snake
1. the blend-smoker is somewhere between the owner of the dog and the swisher-smoker##7
2. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the owner of the dog##5
3. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the ritmeester-smoker##5
4. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the chaman-smoker##7
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
6. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere between the owner of the goldfish and the swisher-smoker##7
7. the owner of the rabbit is on the left or right of the swisher-smoker##3
8. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the blend-smoker##3
9. the ritmeester-smoker is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |    3    |     4     |      5       |
| Cigar   | chaman | vegafina | ritmeester  | blend | swisher |
| Pet           | dog    | goldfish  | hamster | rabbit    | snake        |

