.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-7::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: epic, superhero, zombie, adventure, thriller
5 different pets are kept: cat, dog, frog, hedgehog, rabbit
 1. the owner of the rabbit is not the person watching adventure movies##6
 2. the person watching epic movies is somewhere between the owner of the frog and the owner of the rabbit##7
 3. the person watching adventure movies is on the far left##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is the owner of the frog##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is the person watching zombie movies##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
 9. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
10. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
11. the owner of the dog is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |   2   |       3       |      4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | thriller | superhero | epic | zombie  |
| Pet        | dog     | cat   | frog          | hedgehog    | rabbit |

