.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-8::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, october, december, july, april
5 different pets are kept: dog, hamster, horse, rat, turtle
1. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rat##5
2. the owner of the dog is the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the owner of the turtle##7
5. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the owner of the hamster is not the person who's birthday is in february##6
7. the person who's birthday is in february is the owner of the turtle##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |    3     |  4  |   5    |
| Birthday   | december    | february | october | april | july |
| Pet        | hamster | turtle      | horse    | dog | rat    |

