2. the person eating tomato is between the person eating strawberry and the person driving the skateboard##2
3. the person eating garlic is not the person driving the skateboard##6
4. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
5. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the right of the person driving the helicopter##5
6. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
7. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person driving the jet-ski and the person driving the taxi##7
8. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person eating radish##5
9. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the left of the person eating onion##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Food    | radish  | onion  | tomato  | strawberry | garlic |
| Transport   | helicopter | skateboard | jet-ski | trike | taxi  |

