.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-10::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea, soy-milk
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, thriller, time-travel, satire, animation
 1. the person watching drama movies is the person watching drama movies##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person watching animation movies##6
 3. the person watching satire movies is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person watching drama movies is the person drinking 7up##1
 5. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
 7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 8. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking coffee##7
 9. the person watching thriller movies is not the person drinking coffee##6
10. the person drinking soy-milk is the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |      2      |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | almond-milk | iced-tea | coffee     | 7up       |
| Movie-Genre      | satire   | thriller    | time-travel | animation | drama |

