3. the person who growsballoon-flower is not the person who's hobby is singing##6
4. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who growsiris##2
5. the person who growsorchid is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who growsrose##7
6. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is reading##5
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far right##1
8. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
