3. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the van and the person driving the trike##2
4. the person driving the van is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in may##7
5. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
6. the person driving the van is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##5
7. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##5
8. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in february##7
9. the person who's birthday is in february is the person driving the scooter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |   5    |
| Birthday   | february   | may | october | august | april |
| Transport     | scooter | trike   | tram    | van  | roller |

