 4. the japanese is somewhere between the brazilian and the pakistani##7
 5. the person who likes yellow is somewhere to the right of the brazilian##5
 6. the indian is in an odd position##4
 7. the indian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 8. the pakistani is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
 9. the person who likes green is on the right of the brazilian##1
