.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-16::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  doctor, entrepreneur, manager, nurse, writer
The people use 5 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile, subway, trike, helicopter
 1. the doctor is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
 2. the writer is the person driving the skateboard##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
 4. the person driving the helicopter is the nurse##1
 5. the nurse is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
 6. the doctor is somewhere between the person driving the snowmobile and the writer##7
 7. the doctor is on the left or right of the writer##3
 8. the person driving the helicopter is not the entrepreneur##6
 9. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the entrepreneur##5
10. the doctor is somewhere to the left of the manager##5
11. the person driving the subway is not the entrepreneur##6
12. the person driving the subway is not the writer##6
13. the manager is the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |   2   |   3    |   4    |    5    |
| Job   | entrepreneur | nurse | writer | doctor | manager |
| Transport   | trike       | helicopter | skateboard    | subway | snowmobile    |

