.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-7-20::.
5 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, rat, ferret, pony
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: classical, disco, pop, reggae, soul
1. the owner of the rat is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
2. the fan of soul is the owner of the hedgehog##1
3. the owner of the pony is somewhere between the fan of classical and the fan of soul##7
4. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
5. the owner of the pony is on the right of the fan of disco##1
6. the fan of classical is somewhere to the left of the fan of reggae##5
7. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
8. the owner of the bird is somewhere between the owner of the rat and the fan of classical##7
9. the owner of the rat is the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |    4     |      5      |
| Pet   | ferret   | bird | rat | pony | hedgehog |
| Music-Genre   | classical | reggae | disco   | pop      | soul        |

 